# Brain storming about fix measures in RéTab
Hey there! we are fixating measures in RéTab now!
## What do I want?
- I want RéTab to 
    - have an option for fixating measures
    - make wrongSize Measures red or some shade. with some alert
## What is needed?
- timesignature (or proportion?) must be set
- have an option for fixating measures
    - in `RezTabFile.docSettings` → have a property:  `fixedMeasures` @done
    - update *schema.prisma* accordingly --> with default of `false` @done
        - DB types of front and back must be updated @done
- show timesignature in the begining of the score @done
