        - In both server and client side @done
    - show symbols for 2/2 and 4/4 in Timesignature component @done
- make wrongSize Measures red or some shade. with some alert @done
    - in *MeasureComp.vue* → a coditional class `wrongSize` @done
    -  *Measure* must have a method to validate if it has the right size `Measure.validateSize` @done
- a listener for when the tabgroups are inserted or have their durtaion changed || the getter works as the listener too! @done
- a validator when some MEI file is imported.
    - could be calling *Measure.validateSize* 
- while typing, if the measure tabgroups length is exceeding the measure length: @done
    - automatically go to next measure (make one if it not exists) @done
